query: ALTER TABLE container_registry_repository_manifest ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_repository_manifest_pk PRIMARY KEY(repository_id, manifest_digest), ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_repository_manifest_fk_manifest_digest FOREIGN KEY(manifest_digest) REFERENCES container_registry_manifest(manifest_digest), ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_repository_manifest_fk_repository_id FOREIGN KEY(repository_id) REFERENCES container_registry_repository(id);
